These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, blue, light-blue, turquise
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not the person who likes turquise##6
 5. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person who likes yellow##5
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the person who likes blue##8
 8. the person who likes blue is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 9. the person who likes yellow is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the person who likes blue is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
12. the person who likes blue is in an even position##4
13. the person who likes turquise is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Color    | yellow         | turquise     | light-blue     | blue         |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | writing    | sudoku     | magic-tricks |
| Sport   | cycling       | ice-hockey | volleyball | skiing       |

