.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, italian, indian, american
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, librarian, pilot
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, ice-hockey, weightlifting
 1. the librarian is not to the right of the pilot##8
 2. the indian is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the american is the freelancer##1
 5. the electrician is not the indian##6
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the american is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the indonesian is on the left of the american##1
 9. the american is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
10. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | indian          | indonesian      | american      | italian   |
| Job        | librarian     | electrician | freelancer | pilot      |
| Sport      | weightlifting | baseball    | badminton  | ice-hockey |

