.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, grapes, plum, potato
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, helicopter, ship, bike
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, colombian, dutch
 1. the person eating plum is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 2. the person driving the bike is not the brazilian##6
 3. the colombian is somewhere between the person eating grapes and the person driving the bike##7
 4. the brazilian is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the colombian is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
 8. the dutch is between the person eating blueberry and the colombian##2
 9. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person eating blueberry##8
10. the person eating plum is not to the right of the person eating potato##8
11. the american is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | grapes      | plum      | potato | blueberry |
| Transport   | ship | quad-bike    | bike | helicopter     |
| Nationality   | american    | colombian | dutch  | brazilian |

