4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, davidoff, havana, vegafina
1. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person eating lime##5
2. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person eating lime and the person eating cucumber##7
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
4. the havana-smoker is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the person eating lime is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
7. the person eating lime is the davidoff-smoker##1
8. the person eating lime is somewhere between the vegafina-smoker and the person drinking fanta##7
9. the person eating lime is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | fanta     | coffee | iced-tea  | soy-milk |
| Food          | cranberry | lime   | asparagus | cucumber |
| Cigar   | swisher     | davidoff   | vegafina      | havana      |

