 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person watching family movies##8
 4. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the german is not to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 7. the pakistani is on the left or right of the german##3
 8. the german is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
10. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
11. the german is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
13. the german is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
