1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
3. the person who's sport is swimming is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the snake##2
4. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6
6. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
